Assignment 3
Create a form with fields: name, email, gender, date of birth, and submit button.
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>Registration Form</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">
<h2 align="center">Student Registration Form</h2>
<table align="center" border="1" cellpadding="20" width="50%" bgcolor="#fdfdfd">
<tr>
<td>
<form action="#" method="POST">
<!-- Name -->
<label for="fname"><b>Full Name:</b></label><br>
<input type="text" id="fname" name="fullname" placeholder="Enter full name" required style="width: 100%; padding: 8px;">
<br><br>
<!-- Email -->
<label for="email"><b>Email Address:</b></label><br>
<input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="example@college.edu" required style="width: 100%; padding: 8px;">
<br><br>
<!-- Gender -->
<label><b>Gender:</b></label><br>
<input type="radio" id="male" name="gender" value="Male">
<label for="male">Male</label>
&nbsp;&nbsp;
<input type="radio" id="female" name="gender" value="Female">
<label for="female">Female</label>
<br><br>
<!-- Date of Birth -->
<label for="dob"><b>Date of Birth:</b></label><br>
<input type="date" id="dob" name="dob" style="padding: 5px;">
<br><br>
<!-- Submit Button -->
<center>
<input type="submit" value="Register" style="background-color: green; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; border: none; cursor: pointer;">
&nbsp;&nbsp;
<input type="reset" value="Clear" style="background-color: red; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; border: none; cursor: pointer;">
</center>
</form>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
</body>
</html>
